<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-02-03 01:27 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A5002 &Cx1f; ttd-z
r a BC-HOPPE-OBIT-SFCHRON &LR;      02-03 1897
