<SLUG> BC-GLASS-COLUMN-$ADV06-COX </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
&HT;   
</HEADLINE>
 &HT;    COMMENTARY: BILL GATES GOES WINDOWS SHOPPING
 &HT;    Moving in (k) commentary and (f) financial categories for
release Sunday, Feb. 6.
 &HT;    By ANDREW J. GLASS
 &HT;    c.2000 Cox News Service
