   YANGTZERIVER-CRUISE _ YANGTZE RIVER, China _ A three-day Yangtze
River cruise was the highlight of our 17-day trip to China, a
fascinating study into the contrast between ancient and modern,
natural and man-made, beautiful and destructive. It was a trip
through places that will soon no longer exist. Once the massive
Three Gorges Dam is complete in 2009, the river will rise 50 meters
(approximately 150 feet), enveloping much of the life we saw along
its banks.(Wexler, Atlanta Journal-Constitution freelancer; not for
use by NYTNS clients). WITH PHOTOS.
