   WITH
</P>
<P>
   COMMENTARY: Here is a look at some of the midseason replacement
shows headed toyour television screen in the coming weeks.
(Holloway, Austin American-Statesman)
</P>
<P>
   VIDEO REVIEWS -- Reviews of ``Tarzan,'' ``Stir of Echoes,'' and
