the top bars will look narrower and the bottom bars wider until
your wide-pattern neurons recover.
</P>
<P>
   If these feuding nerve cells have worn you out, remember that
even now your brain is reinvigorating spent nerve cells, fortifying
you for whatever comes next.
</P>
<P>
