<HEADLINE>
FORGET PUTIN. ELECT PRIMAKOV 
</HEADLINE>
   &HT;     (This has already moved to clients of Mikhail Gorbachev's
monthly column. To publish it as a ``separate buy'' article, please
contact your New York Times Syndicate sales representative: 
 &HT;    (--U.S. and Canada: DEBRA WEYDERT in New Jersey at
1-732-390-4480; fax, 732-390-4697. 
