</P>
<P>
   NIRELAND (London) _ Developments in the deteriorating situation
in Northern Ireland: Britain will Thursday announce legislation
giving it the power to suspend Northern Ireland's power-sharing
executive, but will not immediately use the sanction, Prime
Minister Tony Blair's spokesman said. (Summary from wires) By
Warren Hoge.
