While the Dow industrials were down 28 points at 2:10 p.m. EST, the
S&AMP;P 500 index was up 6 and the Nasdaq composite was up 79 points.
The long bond was priced to yield 6.16 percent. By Robert D.
Hershey Jr.
</P>
