   TEN-ARATON-COLUMN (Harare, Zimbabwe) _ Sports of The Times
column: The flip side of tennis in Zimbabwe is evident on the old
avocado farm of Don Black, father of Wayne and Byron Black,
Zimbabwe's top tennis players. It is on this farm that the traces
of the colonial life of Rhodesia are still visible. By Harvey
Araton.
</P>
