   TEN-DAVIS-CUP (Harare, Zimbabwe) _ The Davis Cup draw is set for
the Zimbabwe-U.S. first-round match this weekend. In the Friday
singles, it will be Byron Black against Chris Woodruff and Andre
Agassi against Wayne Black. By Harvey Araton.
</P>
