   ISRAEL-JERUSALEM _ JERUSALEM _ As the deadline for a framework
agreement between Israel and the Palestinians approaches, one of
the more complex and
</P>
<P>
   emotional issues surrounds this Biblical city. But there are
plans developing about how to divide and share Jerusalem.
Developing. (Kaplow, Cox News Service). WITH PHOTO.
