approved a coalition government including the right-wing Freedom
Party of Jorg Haider and will swear in a new chancellor on Friday.
The European Union president says sanctions will take effect on
Friday. Approval of the coalition comes after Haider and Wolfgang
Schuessel of the People's Party, who will be the next chancellor,
