somebody tore my clothes off, I would be furious. Think about it.
Some guy rips off your shirt, and you'd be, like, Wait a minute, I
spent $150 on this shirt!''
</P>
<P>
   -  &UR; Julianne Moore  &LR; on the value of quiet and tender movie love
scenes, in Mirabella.
